    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为老虎机游戏设计一个数据库模型。核心实体应该是GAME，用来存储每局游戏的基本信息，包括game_id和game_name。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GAME",
        "game_id",
        "game_name"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，GAME作为主实体，game_id是主键。那每局游戏会产生多次摇奖吧？需要记录每次摇奖的结果吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GAME",
        "game_id"
