      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，每局游戏包含多次摇奖，我称之为HAND_SUMMARY。它要有hand_number做主键，关联到game_id，还要记录result和amount_won。GAME和HAND_SUMMARY是一对多的关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HAND_SUMMARY",
        "hand_number",
        "game_id",
        "result",
        "amount_won",
        "GAME"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，我在图上加了HAND_SUMMARY，用hand_number做主键，game_id作为外键关联GAME，关系标记为includes。接下来是摇奖的具体细节吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HAND_SUMMARY",
        "hand_number",
        "game_id",
        "GAME",
        "includes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，每个摇奖结果需要详细记录，叫HAND_DETAIL。包括最终轮盘位置final_wheel_position、玩家下注selected_bet、中奖选项winning_option，还有赔率multiplier。HAND_SUMMARY和HAND_DETAIL应该是一对一。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HAND_DETAIL",
        "final_wheel_position",
        "selected_bet",
        "winning_option",
        "multiplier",
        "HAND_SUMMARY"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "HAND_DETAIL也用hand_number做主键，和HAND_SUMMARY一对一关联，用has关系。还有资金流水需要记录吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HAND_DETAIL",
        "hand_number",
        "HAND_SUMMARY",
        "has"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要，每个摇奖会产生交易记录TRANSACTION，有独立的transaction_id做主键，关联hand_number，记录amount_won。HAND_SUMMARY和TRANSACTION是一对一，命名为results_in。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TRANSACTION",
        "transaction_id",
        "hand_number",
        "amount_won",
        "HAND_SUMMARY",
        "results_in"
